Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的結界正在發生異變…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉芳 抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動 莉芳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要更強結界的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正為帝都帶來滅頂之災
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們難道沒意識到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害我親生骨肉的國家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉淪於無窮的絕望和黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊…莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不能就這樣死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她 殺害我們的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 伏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這一刻的到來 我期盼太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 你的力量要為我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是關於信乃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼 我都不想放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為信乃的願望 而喚醒了莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以珠子重新選擇了莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心死我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是就這麼一睡不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一輩子都不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 也不想想我們多辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也好長一段時間都沒有這種提心吊膽的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你能醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從你失去意識之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小信為了奪回珠子去找蒼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找影子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 信乃肯定是拚命把珠子奪了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才會恢復意識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個會耍小聰明的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我越發欣賞你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為我孩子的容器 我要把你帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把信乃交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想違抗我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果交給你 信乃就不再是信乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里見…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是越來越不順了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血還不夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨開始暴走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大勢已去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 信乃會被村雨完全吞噬的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把信乃還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨 快平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現八
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們恐怕也要遭殃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要救信乃只能先阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這是要鬧哪樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被村雨給吞噬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡吧 信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊…介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五狐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…快放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介 已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認出我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 快逃莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上大家 遠離村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了信乃 我才能醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了讓你快逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃過去和我約定過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說今後一定會在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會允許你忘記它的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼難喝的水 真是讓人難以下嚥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 總是讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信信乃絕對會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經 沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃一塹長一智嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和公主的水對抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是信乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…好像終於平息下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兄長大人 真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的結界泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 只有再想其他對策了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬幸我們還有比妖怪還要厲害的四獸神家的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 那智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 難道讓我們做下一輪的「柱」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你嘴裡說出來一點也不像玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 血不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉芳 回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回教會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那智一個人應該對付不了那些老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 那我先回宅子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路一定在擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這個撿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 又得從頭再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人你也相當執著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大人 好好難受啊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識那個女人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是殺了我們的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總感覺在那之前好像在哪兒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了和你一起唱過的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的不是回首過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然八犬士聚齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是義之明珠卻被人帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始再次尋找它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是信乃你的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這樣的話不就和之前一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不完全是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們得到了重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 絕對要把它找出來
